Class SalesMetricsValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netbuilder.model.SalesMetricsValue

  • public class SalesMetricsValue
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will be used like a Product in JavaEE, where we make a new SalesMetricValue for each product each day This will then be added to an ArrayList of SalesMetricValues, to then be printed in the pdf
